{"type":"message","id":"bde0ffe9","parentId":"1f392647","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:45:53.242Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"根据查询结果，`my_work_robot` agent 有自己的独立 workspace：\n\n- **Workspace**: `~\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot`\n- **Agent dir**: `~\\.openclaw\\agents\\my_work_robot\\agent`\n\nOffice Document Specialist Suite 技能安装在主 workspace 的 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` 目录下。\n\n要让 `my_work_robot` 访问到这个技能，有几种方式：\n\n1. **复制技能目录**到 my_work_robot 的 workspace\n2. **创建符号链接**（Windows 上需要管理员权限或使用 mklink）\n3. **重新在 my_work_robot workspace 安装技能**\n\n最简单的方式是重新在 my_work_robot workspace 安装该技能，或者复制过去。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"`my_work_robot` agent **默认访问不到**这个技能。\n\n原因是每个 agent 有自己的独立 workspace：\n- `my_work_robot` 的 workspace：`~\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot`\n- 技能安装在了主 workspace：`~\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\`\n\n**解决方案（三选一）：**\n\n**方案1：重新在 my_work_robot workspace 安装（推荐）**\n```bash\ncd ~\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot\nnpx clawhub install office-document-specialist-suite\n```\n\n**方案2：复制技能目录过去**\n```bash\nxcopy \"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\office-document-specialist-suite\" \"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot\\skills\\office-document-specialist-suite\\\" /E /I\n```\n\n**方案3：让所有 agent 共享主 workspace 的技能（需要改配置）**\n\n要我帮你执行方案1或方案2吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774140341330}}
