{"type":"message","id":"6ceacd74","parentId":"cd2627bc","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:47:02.101Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我了解了配置。根据配置来看：\n\n1. `my_work_robot` agent 有自己的独立 workspace：`C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot`\n2. 主 workspace 是：`C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace`\n\n要让 `my_work_robot` 访问到主 workspace 的技能，有几个方案：\n\n**方案1：修改 agent 配置，让它使用主 workspace**\n需要在 `agents.defaults` 或 `agents.list` 中配置 `my_work_robot` 使用主 workspace。\n\n**方案2：创建符号链接或复制技能**\n把技能复制到 `my_work_robot` 的 workspace。\n\n**方案3：配置共享技能目录**\n看配置中没有直接的 `skills` 共享配置，但可以通过修改 `agents.defaults.workspace` 来让所有 agent 使用同一个 workspace。\n\n最实用的方案是 **方案1**：修改 `my_work_robot` 的配置，让它使用主 workspace 而不是自己的独立 workspace。\n\n\n或者我可以选择复制技能到各个 agent 的 workspace，虽然这样会产生重复代码，但能保持隔离性。我需要修改 `openclaw.json` 文件中的配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据配置分析，`my_work_robot` 默认**访问不到**这个技能，因为它有自己的独立 workspace。\n\n**方案3配置方法：让所有 Agent 共享主 workspace 的技能**\n\n需要修改 `openclaw.json` 配置，有两种方式：\n\n**方式A：修改特定 agent 的 workspace（推荐）**\n\n把 `my_work_robot` 的 workspace 改成主 workspace：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"my_work_robot\",\n        \"name\": \"my_work_robot\",\n        \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\LWS\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\LWS\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\my_work_robot\\\\agent\",\n        \"model\": \"volcengine-plan/ark-code-latest\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**方式B：修改所有 agent 的默认 workspace**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\LWS\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n要我帮你执行方式A的配置修改吗？这样 `my_work_robot` 就能访问主 workspace 的所有技能了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774140401579}}
{"type":"message","id":"c3c29c74","parentId":"6ceacd74","timestamp":"2026-03-22T13:12:01.725Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/LWS/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 22nd, 2026 — 21:12 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-22 13:12 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774185121719}}
